author: jsdelfino
msg: Pass the ModelFactory extension point to the ModelResolvers. This will allow ModelResolvers to create model objects dynamically as part of the resolution process. A first example of this is the WSDLModelResolver which was hardcoding the model factories before. I changed it to use the correct model factories out of the ModelFactory extension point.
